dct_description_sm: This line shapefile represents the major tributaries of the Russian River in California. Line features have attribute codes that represent streams or shorelines. This layer is also intended for users to display major tributaries on maps without seeing all existing tributaries in the Russian River watershed.

The intended purpose of this dataset is to assist in watershed planning and analysis. This layer is also intended for users to display major tributaries on maps without seeing all existing tributaries in the Russian River watershed.
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
